{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/til/02","webpackCompilationHash":"fbc48dc17d95f63beeaf","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"21c98a78-5936-50b4-8462-d43c3327a218","html":"<span class=\"notice\">\n  <em>삽질기 기록!! 추후 계속 디벨롭될 예정이며, 피드백은 언제나 환영입니다.</em>\n</span>\n<h2 id=\"어떤-이유로-진행하게-되었는지\"><a href=\"#%EC%96%B4%EB%96%A4-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A7%84%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B2%8C-%EB%90%98%EC%97%88%EB%8A%94%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"어떤 이유로 진행하게 되었는지 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>어떤 이유로 진행하게 되었는지?</h2>\n<p>이번에 신규 프로젝트로 react-native를 도입하여 진행하게 되었는데 react-native 프로젝트 세팅을 하며 “내가 기존 react로 만들어진 웹 서비스를 작업하며 불편함을 느낀 것은 무엇일까?”라는 고민을 하게되었고, 그 중 하나가 뎁스가 깊어지면 깊어질수록 복잡해지고 지저분해지는 import 방식이여서 어떻게하면 뎁스에 연연하지 않고 깔끔하게 할 수 있을까? 생각했습니다.</p>\n<p>그리하여 생각한 것이 바로 모듈을 활용하여 변수화 시키자! 였고 많은 써치 끝에 사람들이 많이 사용중인 ‘babel-plugin-module-resolver’를 활용하기로 했다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/20ac2/short_image_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.43877551020408%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/images/til/short_image_1.png\"\n        title=\"import 되는 경로를 깔끔하게 하기 위한 삽질기\"\n        src=\"/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/ef0ec/short_image_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/f1791/short_image_1.png 186w,\n/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/e6871/short_image_1.png 373w,\n/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/ef0ec/short_image_1.png 745w,\n/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/a642f/short_image_1.png 1118w,\n/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/4bb54/short_image_1.png 1490w,\n/static/66ec7c6e31cb998b990616ee3cbe062f/20ac2/short_image_1.png 2352w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/babel-plugin-module-resolver\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">babel-plugin-module-resolver</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"진행하기\"><a href=\"#%EC%A7%84%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"진행하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>진행하기</h2>\n<p>설치부터 시작해보자!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save-dev babel-plugin-module-resolver</code></pre></div>\n<p>또는</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> --dev babel-plugin-module-resolver</code></pre></div>\n<p>development 환경에서만 필요하므로 devDependency로 설치해주었다.</p>\n<p>테스트 하기 앞서 다음과 같이 디렉토리 구조를 작성했다.</p>\n<p>매칭 잘 작동하는지 확인하기 위해 디렉토리 구조에 뎁스를 추가했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">src\n  ㄴ component\n    ㄴ depth1\n      ㄴ depth2\n        ㄴ depth3\n          ㄴ Component.tsx\n  ㄴ otherComponent\n    ㄴ OtherComponent.tsx\nassets\n\tㄴ images\n  \tㄴ depth1\n  \t\tㄴ sample-image1.png\n    ㄴ sample-image2.png\nApp.tsx</code></pre></div>\n<p>.babelrc 또는 babel.config.js 파일에 다음과 같이 plugins를 추가해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// .babelrc or babel.config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token string\">'module-resolver'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        root<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        alias<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token string\">'변수명'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'경로'</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 설정을 해주면 된다.</p>\n<p>필자는 다음과 같이 설정을 해주었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// .babelrc or babel.config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token string\">'module-resolver'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        root<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        alias<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token string\">'@components'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/components/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token string\">'@otherComponent'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/otherComponent/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token string\">'@assets'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./assets/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>만약 typescript 를 사용중이라면 tsconfig.json에도 다음과 같이 작성해주자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token comment\">// tsconfig.json</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ...\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"complierOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    ...\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"baseUrl\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"paths\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"@components/*\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"./src/components/*\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"@otherComponent/*\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"./src/otherComponent/*\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"@assets/*\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"./assets/*\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이제 테스트를 한번해보자!</p>\n<p>테스트 방식은 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>App.tsx에서 Component.tsx를 불러온다.</li>\n<li>Component.tsx 내부에는 OtherComponent를 사용한다.</li>\n<li>OtherComponent에서는 assets 폴더 내부에 있는 image들을 사용한다.</li>\n<li>App.tsx에서 Component.tsx를 불러온다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// App.tsx</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Component <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@components/depth1/depth2/depth3/Component'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">App</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Component</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/c6cd9/short_image_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.081309398099261%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAfElEQVQI1yXISw6CMBgAYa7kzg2vKqW/pVWkBaEYEu9/hxHC4ksmk8m9wbkBcRFlXlwby6URijJHdIm0p04qrNRYU2F0gXvUeHs6+iBtRfb0E/7zw8eN3ifeQ2RLA9MUWObImkbm+ey0xL1HvvvrQ0C1HqU76t3NOHJl+AN1wEu5fkThwQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/images/til/short_image_2.png\"\n        title=\"import 되는 경로를 깔끔하게 하기 위한 삽질기\"\n        src=\"/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/ef0ec/short_image_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/f1791/short_image_2.png 186w,\n/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/e6871/short_image_2.png 373w,\n/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/ef0ec/short_image_2.png 745w,\n/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/a642f/short_image_2.png 1118w,\n/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/4bb54/short_image_2.png 1490w,\n/static/8d73ed25760c99693a1ba4f63279806f/c6cd9/short_image_2.png 1894w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>import된 코드에 마우스 커서를 올리면 위와 같이 잘 불러오는 것을 알 수 있다.</p>\n<p><strong>결과화면</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 349px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/928569ad8fc332965bf62c53ed1d43dd/91ea3/short_image_3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 206.30372492836676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/images/til/short_image_3.png\"\n        title=\"import 되는 경로를 깔끔하게 하기 위한 삽질기\"\n        src=\"/static/928569ad8fc332965bf62c53ed1d43dd/91ea3/short_image_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/928569ad8fc332965bf62c53ed1d43dd/f1791/short_image_3.png 186w,\n/static/928569ad8fc332965bf62c53ed1d43dd/91ea3/short_image_3.png 349w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 349px) 100vw, 349px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Component.tsx 내부에는 OtherComponent를 사용한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Component.tsx</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> View <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-native'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> OtherComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@components/otherComponent/OhterComponent'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Component</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">View</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">hello world</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">This is Component</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">OtherComponent</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">View</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Component<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/30e6338f001996ef4e3b85da754e0cfa/12750/short_image_4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.590284142988086%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/images/til/short_image_4.png\"\n        title=\"import 되는 경로를 깔끔하게 하기 위한 삽질기\"\n        src=\"/static/30e6338f001996ef4e3b85da754e0cfa/ef0ec/short_image_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/30e6338f001996ef4e3b85da754e0cfa/f1791/short_image_4.png 186w,\n/static/30e6338f001996ef4e3b85da754e0cfa/e6871/short_image_4.png 373w,\n/static/30e6338f001996ef4e3b85da754e0cfa/ef0ec/short_image_4.png 745w,\n/static/30e6338f001996ef4e3b85da754e0cfa/12750/short_image_4.png 1091w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>VSCode는 친절하게도 Auto import를 제공해준다. 참 똑\u0010똑한 친구인 것 같다.</p>\n<p><strong>결과화면</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce9e87f856f258e133ef461f0978db91/ce404/short_image_5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.467697907188354%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/images/til/short_image_5.png\"\n        title=\"import 되는 경로를 깔끔하게 하기 위한 삽질기\"\n        src=\"/static/ce9e87f856f258e133ef461f0978db91/ef0ec/short_image_5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce9e87f856f258e133ef461f0978db91/f1791/short_image_5.png 186w,\n/static/ce9e87f856f258e133ef461f0978db91/e6871/short_image_5.png 373w,\n/static/ce9e87f856f258e133ef461f0978db91/ef0ec/short_image_5.png 745w,\n/static/ce9e87f856f258e133ef461f0978db91/ce404/short_image_5.png 1099w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>만약 변수설정을 안해주었다면 다음과 같이 불러와졌을 것이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Bad</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> OtherComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'../../../../otherComponent/OhterComponent'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Good</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> OtherComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@otherComponent/OtherComponent'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 @otherComponent를 활용하여 폴더내로 접근이 가능해진다.</p>\n<p>아주 깔끔해졌다!</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>OtherComponent에서는 assets 폴더 내부에 있는 image들을 사용한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> StyleSheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> ScrollView<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Image <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-native'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> sampleImage1 <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@assets/images/depth1/sample-image1.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> sampleImage2 <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@assets/images/sample-image2.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">OtherComponent</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">ScrollView</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">This is OtherComponent</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Image</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">source</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>sampleImage1<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> width<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'100%'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Image</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">source</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>sampleImage2<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> width<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'100%'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">ScrollView</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> OtherComponent<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>필자는 해당 프로젝트에 typesciprt를 사용하고 있어 다음과 같이 경고가 나타난다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 350px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e2b42ad967eea83572baa90c5f8f25a4/ceceb/short_image_6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.71428571428575%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/images/til/short_image_6.png\"\n        title=\"import 되는 경로를 깔끔하게 하기 위한 삽질기\"\n        src=\"/static/e2b42ad967eea83572baa90c5f8f25a4/ceceb/short_image_6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e2b42ad967eea83572baa90c5f8f25a4/f1791/short_image_6.png 186w,\n/static/e2b42ad967eea83572baa90c5f8f25a4/ceceb/short_image_6.png 350w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>“@assets/images/depth1/sample-image1.png”라는 모듈을 찾을 수 없다라는 말인데 이는 typescript 에러 메시지이므로 d.ts를 만들어 png파일을 모듈로 인식하게 해주어 해결했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// file.d.ts</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">declare</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"token string\">'*.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">declare</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"token string\">'*.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>혹시몰라 jpg 확장자까지 같이 해주었다!</p>\n<p>비로서 눈이 편안하게 코딩 할 수 있게 되었다!!</p>\n<p>시간이 된다면 현재 서비스 중인 프로젝트에도 적용해야겠다.</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/til/02","tagSlugs":["/tag/til/","/tag/import/","/tag/babel-plugin-module-resolver/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-02-04","description":"babel-plugin-module-resolver 사용법","tags":["TIL","Import","babel-plugin-module-resolver"],"title":"import 되는 경로를 깔끔하게 하기 위한 삽질기","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/til/02"}}}